OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,FWatch the King's reflection on his
OL,7,Fmother's life in full
OL,9,FThe King has recorded a heartfelt
OL,10,Ftribute to his "darling Mama" to mark
OL,11,Fthe centenary of her birth and praised
OL,12,Fher "steadfast" devotion to "the
OL,13,Fpeople she served."
OL,15,FHe acknowledged the many challenges
OL,16,Fand issues nationally and across the
OL,17,Fglobe that may have caused her reason
OL,18,Ffor concern, and renewed his "own
OL,19,Fsolemn pledge of duty and service to
OL,20,Fyou all".
OL,26,@zD@^OU|D@HO]
