OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,FCharles does not specify which major
OL,7,Fissues he is referring to but since
OL,8,Fthe Queen's death her son Andrew
OL,9,FMountbatten-Windsor has been stripped
OL,10,Fof his titles over his association
OL,11,Fwith convicted sex offender Jeffrey
OL,12,FEpstein.
OL,14,FWorld economies are facing uncertainty
OL,15,Ffollowing the US and Israel's war
OL,16,Fagainst Iran, which has triggered
OL,17,Fspikes in the oil price and affected
OL,18,Fglobal shipping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
