OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine has
OL,7,Fentered its fifth year and the rise of
OL,8,Fsocial media is having a negative
OL,9,Feffect on the young, critics believe.
OL,11,FQueen Elizabeth II died peacefully at
OL,12,Fher Balmoral home aged 96 on September
OL,13,F8 2022, after serving as sovereign for
OL,14,F70 years - the longest reign in
OL,15,FBritish history and among the longest
OL,16,Fin world history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
