OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,FShe became one of the most iconic
OL,7,Ffaces of the 20th century, epitomising
OL,8,Fmuch that was identified as British,
OL,9,Fwhile at home her love of horses and
OL,10,Fdogs defined the Queen as much as her
OL,11,Frole as head of state.
OL,13,FIn the video tribute, filmed in the
OL,14,Flibrary at Balmoral Castle in early
OL,15,FApril, the King adds: "Queen
OL,16,FElizabeth's promise with destiny kept'
OL,17,Fshaped the world around her and
OL,18,Ftouched the lives of countless people
OL,19,Facross our nation, the Commonwealth
OL,20,Fand beyond.
OL,26,@wD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
