PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776798670
OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,F"Her near-century was one of
OL,7,Fremarkable change and yet, through
OL,8,Feach passing decade, through every
OL,9,Ftransformation, she remained constant,
OL,10,Fsteadfast and wholly devoted to the
OL,11,Fpeople she served.
OL,13,F"Millions will remember her for
OL,14,Fmoments of national significance; many
OL,15,Fothers for a fleeting personal
OL,16,Fencounter, a smile, a kind word that
OL,17,Flifted spirits ... or for that
OL,18,Fmarvellous twinkle of the eye when
OL,19,Fsharing a marmalade sandwich with
OL,20,FPaddington Bear in the final months of
OL,21,Fher life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
