OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,FThe highlight of the events will see
OL,7,Fthe royal family gather for a
OL,8,FBuckingham Palace reception with
OL,9,Fcharities and organisations associated
OL,10,Fwith the late Queen invited, including
OL,11,FCancer Research UK, the Jockey Club
OL,12,Fand the Army Benevolent Fund.
OL,14,FGuests will include some of the UK's
OL,15,Foldest citizens celebrating their
OL,16,F100th birthday on April 21, with the
OL,17,FKing presenting their centenary cards
OL,18,Fin-person.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
