FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776798670
OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,F"So, young or old, and whatever our
OL,7,Fdifferences, let us therefore seek to
OL,8,Ffollow this example as we make today
OL,9,Fnot the marking of a milestone felt by
OL,10,Fabsence but the celebration of a life
OL,11,Fwell-lived, and a legacy of hope, as
OL,12,Fwe strive together towards a 'better,
OL,13,Fhappier tomorrow' ` one rooted in
OL,14,Fpeace, justice, prosperity and
OL,15,Fsecurity," he said.
OL,17,FHe ended by addressing his mother:
OL,18,F"God bless you, darling Mama; you
OL,19,Fremain forever in our hearts and
OL,20,Fprayers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@JO]zD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
