OL,3,CKing leads tributes to Queen Elizabeth
OL,4,CII on her centenary
OL,6,FDuring the day, members of the
OL,7,Fmonarchy will visit the British Museum
OL,8,Fto see a scale model of the Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth Memorial with architect Lord
OL,10,FFoster, who won the bid to design the
OL,11,Fnational monument, during a reception
OL,12,Fattended by the prime minister.
OL,14,FThe memorial will also feature a
OL,15,F"family of gardens" through St James's
OL,16,FPark with meandering paths and a new
OL,17,Ftranslucent, glass unity bridge.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@SO]
